{
  "id": "69bea71441df0dacd6940f78",
  "title": "歯ブラシの交換時期",
  "created": 1774102295,
  "updated": 1774124063,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "69bea71441df0dacd6940f78",
      "text": "歯ブラシの交換時期",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1774102295,
      "updated": 1774102295
    },
    {
      "id": "69bea7160000000000e372cf",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1774102295,
      "updated": 1774102295
    },
    {
      "id": "69bea7170000000000e372d0",
      "text": "[Mijikko.icon]",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1774102295,
      "updated": 1774102296
    },
    {
      "id": "69bea7170000000000e372d2",
      "text": "\tブラシが横に開いてから交換したほうが良いって話する人もいるけど…",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1774102296,
      "updated": 1774102337
    },
    {
      "id": "69bea7280000000000e372d3",
      "text": "\t[雑菌]増えるので１ヶ月ぐらいが目安",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1774102312,
      "updated": 1774102326
    },
    {
      "id": "69bea7350000000000e372d4",
      "text": "\t\tだったはず",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1774102326,
      "updated": 1774102328
    },
    {
      "id": "69bea7460000000000e372d5",
      "text": "\t\t別に高くもなんとも無いので気軽に交換するのが良い",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1774102342,
      "updated": 1774102354
    },
    {
      "id": "69bea7170000000000e372d1",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1774102296,
      "updated": 1774102296
    },
    {
      "id": "69bece1900000000006c8bf4",
      "text": "[yosider.icon]",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1774112282,
      "updated": 1774112283
    },
    {
      "id": "69bece1b00000000006c8bf6",
      "text": " 雑菌がいやなので毎回泡ハンドソープつけて洗ってる",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1774112284,
      "updated": 1774112327
    },
    {
      "id": "69bece1900000000006c8bf5",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1774112282,
      "updated": 1774112282
    },
    {
      "id": "69befbfa0000000000c828ce",
      "text": "[sta.icon]",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1774124026,
      "updated": 1774124027
    },
    {
      "id": "69befbfb0000000000c828cf",
      "text": "\t気にしてなかった",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1774124027,
      "updated": 1774124033
    },
    {
      "id": "69befc0e0000000000c828d0",
      "text": "\t実家に歯ブラシは何十本とストックしてあるのを思い出した",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1774124046,
      "updated": 1774124057
    },
    {
      "id": "69befc180000000000c828d1",
      "text": "\t\tこれは極端だが、もっと気軽に変えてもいいかもなぁ",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1774124057,
      "updated": 1774124063
    },
    {
      "id": "69befbfa0000000000c828cd",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1774124026,
      "updated": 1774124026
    },
    {
      "id": "69becdec00000000006c8bf2",
      "text": "[歯ブラシ]",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1774112238,
      "updated": 1774112240
    },
    {
      "id": "69becdf000000000006c8bf3",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1774112240,
      "updated": 1774112240
    }
  ]
}